{"tid":1335331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8月3日＜旺角再遊行＞最新消息","createTime":"2019-07-20T12:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T14:20:24.000Z","uid":279009,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"430b609fdcb48f34ccd8f410067f882457f631cf","tid":1335331,"uid":279009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:59:29.000Z","msg":"各位好，旺角網民已就8月3日(星期六)＜旺角再遊行＞向警方提交不反對通知書，目前正在磋議遊行路線嘅最終定案。<br />\n由於主要用嚟發佈消息嘅平台「旺角人旺角事」專頁因為長期被打壓及監察導致失去好多功能，管理員暫時未能夠喺專頁發佈任何消息。<br />\n有見及此，「旺角人旺角事」目前開咗一個facebook group，以發佈有關8月3日＜旺角再遊行＞嘅最新消息，希望各位多多關注，8月3日旺角見!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDjZjV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDjZjV5.jpg&h=14926258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rvHgm9r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrvHgm9r.jpg&h=43d04d78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c1ff864f0913855113b473f40ee27db982083ac","tid":1335331,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2938719aef1a6008f5dd87167ab7c0eb420a2684","tid":1335331,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:12:47.000Z","msg":"呢場係主線任務 大家做好文宣"},{"pid":"94d5dc4ee0ff0b7f608d470365629ac709c25dae","tid":1335331,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:14:17.000Z","msg":"打響8月頭炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5b4c33259af4f908e3e34c8cff46ab263e1101","tid":1335331,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:36:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d71e89381b6bebeec2922d17ddb1769b22902e18","tid":1335331,"uid":186509,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:39:11.